{"books":[{"id":"whb","name":"文汇报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"学好文件抓住纲　深入揭批“四人帮”","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1977,"month":4,"day":2}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040101.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>毛主席选定接班人，革命遗志得继承；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席含笑挥巨手，抓纲治国向前进。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040102.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>学大寨春汛起波涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库工地笑浪高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华主席讲话鼓东风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎春大干掀高潮。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040103.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>两个文件威力大，纲举目张批‘四害’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高擎红旗志更坚，步调一致朝前迈。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040104.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>虎狼在前怒满腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重任在肩练武忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声号令挟雷电，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮林织下歼敌网。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040105.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>新厂巍巍耸云霄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们工人斗志高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习大庆创新业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吊臂疾书红喜报。</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040106.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>秧壮谨防害虫咬，田肥也须勤锄草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈开阔步学大寨，田头批判先开炮!</FONT>"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<IMG alt=请插入7号盘，按F5键刷新后显示本插图！ src=\"D:\\inset\\1977\\04\\7742040107.JPG\">"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"<FONT class=imgsm>嗓门一拉如炮开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万钧雷霆出胸怀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深揭猛批“四人帮”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工地就是审判台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(本报通讯　员绘画配诗)</FONT>"}],"comments":[],"origin":"本报","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"四人帮","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}